description: This file defines a React functional component named `Tabs` which renders a tabbed navigation UI with accessibility features, allowing switching between different tabs based on provided props.

methods.name: Tabs({ tabs, active, onChange })
methods.description: React functional component that renders a tab bar with active tab indication. Accepts props: 'tabs' (array of tab objects), 'active' (current active tab id), and 'onChange' (callback for tab change).
